    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Sensors AI Assistant\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to help you explore different sensors, their usage, and the data type(s) they collect.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n*Provide a Data Type*: Ask the assistant to describe sensors that might collect a specific type of data.\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure what to ask?**]\r\nTry a prompt like this:\r\n> What kinds of sensors could I use to collect **biometric** data?\r\n\r\n:::\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n*Provide a Computer System or Device*: Ask about what sensors might be present in certain systems or devices and about the type of data that they produce.\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure what to ask?**]\r\nTry a prompt like this:\r\n> I have an iPhone 16 and I want to know what kinds of sensors it has and how what kinds of data they produce.\r\n\r\n:::\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n*Suggest a situation*: Share an idea, problem, or challenge that you have encountered and ask about how sensors and data might be used to help.\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure what to ask?**]\r\nTry a prompt like this:\r\n> I'm trying to automate the restocking the school vending machines-- what sensors might help with that?\r\n:::\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n*Keep Learning*: Feel free to ask \"why\" or \"how\" questions to deepen your understanding of sensors and data.\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure what to ask?**]\r\nTry a prompt like this:\r\n> Can you give me more information on how radar works?\r\n:::\r\n&nbsp;\r\n",
